### Warnings (auto-handled)
- [c001] Tailwind CSS v4 syntax must be used - v2/v3 syntax (bg-opacity-*, bg-gradient-to-*) is forbidden
  Recommendation: Use v4 syntax: bg-white/50 instead of bg-opacity-50, use color utilities directly instead of gradients
- [c002] Direct IndexedDB or Supabase access is forbidden - must go through DataService
  Recommendation: Import and use DataService from '@/services/data/DataService' for all data operations
- [c003] LLM API calls must go through ai-assistant Edge Function - direct LLM API calls forbidden
  Recommendation: Use the Agent SSE client in '@/lib/agent/sseClient.ts' for AI interactions
- [c005] SQL changes must be centralized in app/supabase/setup.sql - no separate SQL files
  Recommendation: Add all schema changes to setup.sql and update SUPABASE_COOKBOOK.md
